Show HN: NeonFin – Manage your personal finances and budgets
text:
Hey HN!

We've been working tirelessly for the last few months to perfect neonFin: We know how frustrating it can be to use budgeting apps that just don't give you the information and analytics you need to truly take control of your finances. That's why we've created neonFin - the ultimate budget book app that offers powerful tools to help you make sense of your spending and achieve your financial goals.

With neonFin, you'll enjoy features like:

Effortless expense tracking with our AI-powered receipt scanning feature that allows you to add new purchases to your budget in just seconds.

Understanding what you are actually buying with the integration of detailed information about products, like the share of vegan products, CO2 emissions, price changes, and more.

Advanced analytics in real-time to help you track your expenses by category and see your spending habits over time.

Create budgets for different aspects of your life like CO2 emissions, average nutriscore, and more.

We believe that with neonFin, you'll have everything you need to take control of your finances, and we can't wait to hear your thoughts about our app!
